A moment, a blink of an eye
To be identified, to be determined
To strike, to beat, to hit
To examine, to study, to investigate, to analyze
To be founded, to be established
To influence, to impress, to affect
To hire, to lease, to rent
To be asked for, to be desired
To search, to look for; to call
To get lost, to be lost
To him; to her; to it
Those/the one later; the next one
With him; with her; with it
To arrive, to reach, to attain
May it come easy to you
